1. create one folder as server
2. then cd the folder
3. npm init
4. npm i
5. npm i express
6. npm i mongoose
there are five methode like curd in mongo they are: 
1.post:send,
2.get:get,
3.delete:delete,
4.put:update,
5.patch :small update 

7.install (nodemon) not to restart again and again after editing in server(npm i -g nodemon)
8.after installing nodemon run the code in (nodemon filename) instead of (node filename)
